INSTALLING I3
=============

1) install i3 and git
$ sudo apt install i3 git

2) clone this repo
$ git clone https://github.com/dasty/i3-config.git ~/.i3

3) log out and login again using i3

FINISHING INSTALLATION
======================

1) install extra needed packages
$ sudo apt install xautolock vim undistract-me light

2) add yourself to group video
$ sudo vigr

3) add following lines to .bashrc

cat << '-----EOF-----' >> ~/.bashrc
export EDITOR=vim

# get notification when longer command finishes
source /etc/profile.d/undistract-me.sh
-----EOF-----

TIPS
====

XDG_CURRENT_DESKTOP=GNOME gnome-control-center
